<%@ page contentType="text/html;charset=UTF-8" language="java" trimDirectiveWhitespaces="true" %>
<div class="page">
    <div class="swiper-container swiper-container-horizontal">
        <ul class="swiper-wrapper">
            <li class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="guide-pic">
                    <img class="swiper-lazy" data-src="<%=webServer%>static/images/guide/1-1.jpg"/>
                    <div class="swiper-lazy-preloader"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="desc-container">
                    <div class="desc-body">
                        <h2>功能介绍</h2>

                        <div class="text-center">
                            <p>主动拍摄录制题目，随心所讲</p>

                            <p>纪录下你认为值得被听到的声音</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="guide-pic">
                    <img class="swiper-lazy" data-src="<%=webServer%>static/images/guide/1-2.jpg"/>
                    <div class="swiper-lazy-preloader"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="desc-container">
                    <div class="desc-body">
                        <h2>拍题</h2>

                        <div>
                            <p>步骤1：</p>

                            <p>先调整焦距让题目清晰，再<em>横屏</em>拍摄题目</p>

                            <p>步骤2：</p>

                            <p>选择适合区域，每次只能截取<em>1</em>道题目</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="guide-pic">
                    <img class="swiper-lazy" data-src="<%=webServer%>static/images/guide/1-3.jpg"/>
                    <div class="swiper-lazy-preloader"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="desc-container">
                    <div class="desc-body">
                        <h2>待录制列表</h2>

                        <div class="text-center">
                            <p>最近拍摄的题目默认排在第1条</p>

                            <p>选择需要录制的题目进行录制</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="guide-pic">
                    <img class="swiper-lazy" data-src="<%=webServer%>static/images/guide/1-4.jpg"/>
                    <div class="swiper-lazy-preloader"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="desc-container">
                    <div class="desc-body">
                        <h2>选择讲解方式</h2>

                        <div>
                            <p>白板：适于讲解复杂的数理化题目建议在平板等大屏环境下操作</p>

                            <p>音频：适于不带图形等用语音即可说明白的题目</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="guide-pic">
                    <img class="swiper-lazy" data-src="<%=webServer%>static/images/guide/1-5.jpg"/>
                    <div class="swiper-lazy-preloader"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="desc-container">
                    <div class="desc-body">
                        <h2>白板录制</h2>

                        <div>
                            <p>先调整题目尺寸到合适的大小，然后确定开始录制。可以选择左侧工具栏的不同颜色画笔，出现误操作时可以使用橡皮擦（录制时间不低于5秒，不超过30分钟）</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="guide-pic">
                    <img class="swiper-lazy" data-src="<%=webServer%>static/images/guide/1-6.jpg"/>
                    <div class="swiper-lazy-preloader"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="desc-container">
                    <div class="desc-body">
                        <h2>音频录制</h2>

                        <div class="text-center">
                            <p>音频录制过程中支持暂停功能</p>

                            <p>录制完成后点击完成</p>

                            <p>（录制时间不低于5秒，不得超过15分钟）</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="guide-pic">
                    <img class="swiper-lazy" data-src="<%=webServer%>static/images/guide/1-7.jpg"/>
                    <div class="swiper-lazy-preloader"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="desc-container">
                    <div class="desc-body">
                        <h2>已录制列表</h2>

                        <div>
                            <p>录制完成后，点击上传按钮就可以在已录制列表中查看题目详情、学生购买情况</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
    </div>
</div>